Is the above really a "variety of the Āryā metre"? Only one mora is missing. 
-->
        <!-- 
BD: I've thought for a bit about this, but can't find a good solution. I'm pretty sure it is indeed āryā, but either it is unmetrical (in addition to the missing mora, there is no caesura in the first line), or it is incorrectly read/inscribed. I can't improve the reading or offer a plausible emendation. 
-->
