cā is suspicious; unmetrical 
-->
          <l n="c"><lb n="14"/>senāpatinā kal<choice>
              <unclear>pitā </unclear>
              <unclear>yāṇa-</unclear>
            </choice></l>
          <l n="d">mālinehālpa-buddhinā||</l>
